collections.name: Kareem
collections.description: Artist, known professionally as Andrew Kareem, is a digital and graphic artist. In his art, he uses various media to create phantasmagoric works that make social reflections using figures and situations from modern times as references. Kareem's art challenges the notion of traditional art forms and explores the intersection between technology, pop culture, consumerism. This artist represents a vision of the vast and ever-expanding world of digital art, pushing the limits of what is possible with technology and artistic expression. Kareem explores the theme of human change, reflection and the relationship between virtual and tangible worlds. His works explore themes of memory, identity and the interaction between humans and machines. Kareem's work forces the viewer to consider the impact of technology on identity, relationships, and social norms. In recent years we have witnessed an unprecedented upheaval of the world as we knew it. For the first time, however...

collections.name: Orsi Cyberpunk
collections.description: Orsi Cyberpunk Equine is a digital art project that reimagines the elegance of the Akhal-Teke horse through a futuristic cybernetic lens. Blending organic beauty with neon-lit circuitry, this project transforms the horse into a biomechanical marvel—its golden coat infused with glowing cyberpunk energy, fiber-optic mane, and AI-enhanced eyes. A fusion of nature and technology, Cyberpunk Equine captures the spirit of speed, intelligence, and innovation in a world where the digital and the organic collide.

collections.name: JUST A BEAN
collections.description:
Just A Bean is more than just a coffee label - it's a movement that redefines the enjoyment of high-quality coffee with digital art and cutting-edge technology.
Each roast is transparently documented in the blockchain, so our customers always know exactly when their coffee was roasted and receive all relevant details about their individual batch. This transparency creates trust and connects us even more closely with our customers.

Our loyalty program rewards customers with a JAB token for every purchase and allows them to benefit from exclusive offers and advantages by reaching different levels. The points collected can be used on the next purchase, so that customers can pay for their coffee partially or completely with their JAB points. This gives our customers the freedom to actively shape their coffee enjoyment and enjoy additional benefits. After a certain amout of pruchase the customer receives a special NFT so he can built up his own JAB Collection
